!!!5
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: 'text/html; charset=UTF-8', :'http-equiv' => 'Content-Type'}
  %body
    %h1 You joined a team for the 2017 DEF CON CTF Quals
    :markdown
      Thanks for joining a team in the 2017 DEF CON CTF. Here are your team's
      details:

      Name: #{@team.name}

      A copy of this message has been forwarded to your honorable captain,
      #{@user.username}.

      ## What's next for #{@newbie.username}?

      Nothing until the competition! Thanks again for signing up!

      ## What's next for #{@user.username}?

      Make sure the rest of your team gets registered. If you don't know this
      new exciting team member of yours, you have a terrible password or an
      opsec problem, and you should contact us about it.
